Fighting to prevent the fall of society, the agents will find themselves caught in an epic conspiracy, forced to combat not only the effects of a manmade virus, but also the rising threat of those behind it. When everything collapes, your mission begins.

description:
The Story Of Keanu.

What's up dawgs, this is the story of Keanu! The Story of Keanu

Rules are pretty basic, just be a good person.

Now before I list off the rules I would like to explain to you why I added in these rules.

1. To make sure that this stream is fun and enjoyable.

2. There is no reason why you wouldn't follow these basic rules to begin with.

3. We are here to have fun and enjoy talking/gaming together, please don't ruin it.

Now here are the rules for my stream, I will be adding in more if I see issues.

I find number 1 to be the most important rule, I would recommend following it!

1. Enjoy yourself!

2. Don't share your stream on my stream unless I give you permission to do so.

name: Let's go on a journey in Space!
description:
Daily Stream Description:

Let's play some Elite Dangerous! It's a really cool game! Link to music that is now playing: https://soundcloud.com/odesza

About the stream:

I am an amateur osu! player that enjoys everyone that stops by and watches me play. I really appreciate it, because my viewers are what makes this channel. If you couldn't tell, I love the Pokémon Dunsparce. Osu! Profile: dunspace234

About Osu!:

Many of you may be asking: "What the heck is this?" To answer you that question, it is a rhythm game, relate it to Guitar Hero if it helps. People make songs of whatever they would like (mostly Japanese because we're all nerds here :p) and post them for other people to play. The goal is to lpay the song as accurately as you can to get the best score, resulting in the best rank. I play this game using a Drawing Tablet, which helps me guide my cursor across the screen, instead of a mouse.

Chat Rules:

  • DONT REQUEST DIFFICULT SONGS. I am rank ~200,000. Give me a break guys XD
  • Be nice to each other. The internet can be a very fun place when everyone is being nice to each other, so let's all enjoy our stay and be nice :)
  • Post links your cool uncle would approve of >.> If is anything too extreme I will ban the link.
  • Good grammar. I don't require this in my chat but yknow, take the small bit of effort to capitalize and put commas and periods and sort. It makes you look smart and I appreciate the effort ;)

Osu! Stuff:

  • Tablet: CTH - 470
  • Tablet Area: Alittle less than full :)
  • Osu! Resolution: 1200x800 to make the stream look nice :)
  • Keyboard: CM Storm QuickFire TK - Blue Switches

type.name: No Man's Sky
type.description:
No Man’s Sky is a game about exploration and survival in an infinite procedurally generated galaxy.Whether a distant mountain or a planet hanging low on the horizon, you can go there. You can fly seamlessly from the surface of a planet to another, and every star in the sky is a sun that you can visit.Explore uncharted solar systems and catalogue unique new forms of life. Every planet’s landscape is different from the next, and populated by species never before encountered.Find ancient artefacts that could reveal the secrets behind the universe.
Choose whether to share your discoveries with other players. They’re exploring the same vast universe in parallel; perhaps you’ll make your mark on their worlds as well as your own.

Clearly tonight I've opted to play a scary game...that means you probably shouldn't wear headphones. #JustSayin...

type.name: Call of Duty: Black Ops III
type.description:
Call of Duty: Black Ops III is the 2015 installment of the Call of Duty franchise by Treyarch and Sledgehammer games, it is also the sequel to Treyarchs 2012 game Black Ops II.

Black Ops III, is unlike any other Call of Duty ever made before this is because Black Ops III (aka. BO3) has a more open world Campaign letting you in theroy make your own way to objectives and complete the missions more "freely". Furthermore, Black Ops 3 will have a Co-Op Campaign with up to four players in it you will have, like multiplayer, a custom player of your own where you can edit the classes and upgrade it as you would like freely so Team Up, Load Guns and Destroy Everything blocking your path.

Black Ops III has a scheduled release date of 6th November 2015 for Xbox One, PlayStation 4, PC as well as last generation platforms such as the Xbox 360 and the PlayStation 3 but will have no campaign and will limited to 30fps. 

"Most Anticipated Call of Duty ever made" - RapidFireGaming

Minecraft is a procedurally-generated game of world exploration, resource harvesting, and freeform construction. Minecraft supports local and online multiplayer, and features are being added regularly.

So far more than 19 million people have bought the PC/Mac version of the game as of June 21, 2015.
An official wiki exists at http://minecraft.gamepedia.com

Minecraft has influenced a plethora of its users to go beyond the simple voxel block to make the most extraordinary creations. Mod authors have even taken this push to the next level as they are continuously creating mods that allow for more innovation while simultaneously retaining the core concept of the game - breaking and placing blocks...

*You are entering a judgement free zone. Be yourself. Anyone (except assholes) is welcome.*

My overlay is done by the lovely phone_microwave. If you haven't checked him out please do so! He's awesome and he's always up for making an overlay or graphics for someone. :)


Toast is a 25 year old who lives in boring ol' Alabama. Her first game console was a Super Nintendo. She started PC gaming in February 2012 and can't seem to get enough of it. She started streaming on Beam on March 12th 2016. Toast has 3 slightly evil dogs and 1 furry spawn of Satan more commonly known as a cat. You'll often hear them in the background because they love to bark and meow at absolutely anything and everything.



In true Beam fashion we support other streamers on this channel! I've listed just a few of them below. Just click on their names to check them out. :)

type.name: Brawlhalla
type.description:
Brawlhalla: An eternal battle arena where the greatest warriors in history brawl to prove who's the best that ever was, is, or will be. Competitors from all eras slug it out in devious and challenging arenas. Every match is an epic test of skill, speed, and strength, and every victory brings added glory and bragging rights to the winners. 

Clockwork VALKRIs salt these slugfests with powerful weapons and gadgets. Fighters scramble to grab swords, hammers, blasters, rocket lances and more! Every weapon changes your play style and your options. Gadgets like mines, bombs, and spiked spheres add even more danger into the mix, letting fighters change the course of battle with a well timed-throw or carefully laid trap.
